---
import HorizontalDivider from "@components/utils/HorizontalDivider.astro";
---

<div
  class="bg-gradient-to-b flex flex-col gap-24 mb-8 from-yellow-500/90 to-transparent py-6 rounded-t-[100px]"
>
  <h1 class="text-white text-center py-28 text-5xl font-designer">
    ¿Cómo Iniciar con nosotros?
  </h1>
</div>

<main class="flex flex-col gap-y-8 items-center">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-[1fr_1px_1fr] items-center h-screen">
    <div
      class="flex gap-8 sticky top-0 justify-center items-baseline phase my-24 self-start"
    >
      <span
        class="text-[190px] font-roboto font-bold text-center text-yellow-500 drop-shadow-md [text-shadow:0_0_20px_#fc0]"
        >1</span
      >
      <span
        class="text-6xl font-roboto [text-shadow:0px_0px_20px_#ffffffee] font-semibold text-white"
        >Fase Uno</span
      >
    </div>
    <HorizontalDivider color="yellow" />
    <div class="flex flex-col px-8 font-semibold gap-y-16 text-center">
      <img class="rotate" src="images/Platforms.webp" alt="" />
      <p class="text-white">
        Selecciona tu carrera o curso corto de tu interés, y solicita a nuestros
        asesores toda la información que necesites. Ellos podrán suministrarte
        detalles sobre:
      </p>

      <div class="flex gap-10 flex-wrap items-center justify-center text-white">
        <span
          class="border text-pretty font-semibold -skew-x-3 rounded-full px-6 py-2 [text-shadow:1px_0px_10px_#fd4] [box-shadow:1px_0px_10px_#fd4] border-yellow-500"
          >Duracion</span
        >
        <span
          class="border text-pretty font-semibold -skew-x-3 rounded-full px-6 py-2 [text-shadow:1px_0px_10px_#fd4] [box-shadow:1px_0px_10px_#fd4] border-yellow-500"
          >Fecha de Inicio</span
        >
        <span
          class="border text-pretty font-semibold -skew-x-3 rounded-full px-6 py-2 [text-shadow:1px_0px_10px_#fd4] [box-shadow:1px_0px_10px_#fd4] border-yellow-500"
          >Pensun</span
        >
        <span
          class="border text-pretty font-semibold -skew-x-3 rounded-full px-6 py-2 [text-shadow:1px_0px_10px_#fd4] [box-shadow:1px_0px_10px_#fd4] border-yellow-500"
          >Valor</span
        >
        <span
          class="border text-pretty font-semibold -skew-x-3 rounded-full px-6 py-2 [text-shadow:1px_0px_10px_#fd4] [box-shadow:1px_0px_10px_#fd4] border-yellow-500"
          >Formas de pago</span
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-[1fr_1px_1fr] items-center h-screen">
    <div class="flex flex-col px-8 font-semibold gap-5 text-center">
      <img class="rotate" src="images/Platforms.webp" alt="" />
      <p class="text-white">
        Selecciona tu carrera o curso corto de tu interés, y solicita a nuestros
        asesores toda la información que necesites. Ellos podrán suministrarte
        detalles sobre:
      </p>
    </div>

    <HorizontalDivider color="yellow" />

    <div
      class="flex gap-8 sticky top-0 justify-center items-baseline phase-reverse my-24 self-start"
    >
      <span
        class="text-[190px] font-roboto font-bold text-center text-yellow-500 drop-shadow-md [text-shadow:0_0_20px_#fc0]"
        >2</span
      >
      <span
        class="text-6xl font-roboto [text-shadow:0px_0px_20px_#ffffffee] font-semibold text-white"
        >Fase Dos</span
      >
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-[1fr_1px_1fr] items-center h-screen">
    <div
      class="flex gap-8 sticky top-0 justify-center items-baseline phase my-24 self-start"
    >
      <span
        class="text-[190px] font-roboto font-bold text-center text-yellow-500 drop-shadow-md [text-shadow:0_0_20px_#fc0]"
        >3</span
      >
      <span
        class="text-6xl font-roboto [text-shadow:0px_0px_20px_#ffffffee] font-semibold text-white"
        >Fase Tres</span
      >
    </div>
    <HorizontalDivider color="yellow" />
    <div class="flex flex-col px-8 font-semibold gap-5 text-center">
      <img class="rotate" src="images/Platforms.webp" alt="" />
      <p class="text-white">
        Selecciona tu carrera o curso corto de tu interés, y solicita a nuestros
        asesores toda la información que necesites. Ellos podrán suministrarte
        detalles sobre:
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
